Carragher: &quot;If I was Klopp and someone said to me you can go out and get Joe Hart in January, I would do it.&quot;<br />
<br />
Carragher: &quot;The position Liverpool are in, if they get offered a goalkeeper in January who has won titles like Joe Hart, I'd go &amp; get him.&quot;

Pulisic: &quot;I think with soccer, you never really know what's going to happen in your career &mdash; that's the beauty of it.&quot;<br />
<br />
Pulisic: &quot;Right now, I'm with Dortmund and very happy. I'm earning my spot and working hard for that team.&quot;
